import React from 'react';
import {Menu} from 'semantic-ui-react';

export default () => {
    return (
        <Menu style={{ marginTop: '1em'}}>
            <Menu.Item>
                MicrogridEther
            </Menu.Item>

            <Menu.Menu position="right">
                <Menu.Item>
                    New Auction
                </Menu.Item>
                <Menu.Item>
                    Enter An Auction
                </Menu.Item>
                <Menu.Item>
                    Campaigns
                </Menu.Item>
            </Menu.Menu>
        </Menu>
    )
}
